---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---
<Base
  title="The Atelier — Candle Atelier"
  description="A small London studio pouring coconut-rapeseed wax in hand-finished vessels."
>
  <section class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 py-20 md:px-10 md:py-28">
    <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.32em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">The Atelier</div>
    <h1 class="mt-4 font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-5xl text-[color:var(--color-bone)] md:text-7xl">A quiet practice.</h1>

    <div class="mt-14 grid gap-14 md:grid-cols-[1.1fr_1fr]">
      <div class="space-y-6 text-[color:var(--color-bone-dim)] leading-relaxed">
        <p>Candle Atelier began in a basement in South London, with one pot, one thermometer, and a very specific kind of impatience for candles that announced themselves too loudly.</p>
        <p>Every candle is poured by hand in batches of no more than forty. We use a coconut-rapeseed wax blend for its clean, even burn, and cotton wicks that crackle just faintly. Fragrances are built in-house, then left to cure for two full weeks before we send them out — you can taste the difference.</p>
        <p>We keep the range small on purpose. Four candles, four rooms, four moods. When the season turns, we pour four more.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="space-y-10">
        <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-ink-line)] pt-6">
          <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Wax</div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-bone)]">Coconut-rapeseed blend</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Clean burn, low soot, vegan.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-ink-line)] pt-6">
          <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Wick</div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-bone)]">Braided cotton</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Untreated. Never lead-core.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="border-t border-[color:var(--color-ink-line)] pt-6">
          <div class="text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[0.22em] text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Cure time</div>
          <div class="mt-2 font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-2xl text-[color:var(--color-bone)]">14 days minimum</div>
          <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-bone-mute)]">Patience is the fragrance.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-24 border-t border-[color:var(--color-ink-line)] pt-10">
      <h2 class="font-[family-name:var(--font-display)] text-3xl text-[color:var(--color-bone)]">The principles</h2>
      <ul class="mt-8 grid gap-6 text-[color:var(--color-bone-dim)] md:grid-cols-2">
        <li class="border-l border-[color:var(--color-ember)] pl-5">Small batch over big run.</li>
        <li class="border-l border-[color:var(--color-ember)] pl-5">Scent that stays under the furniture, not over it.</li>
        <li class="border-l border-[color:var(--color-ember)] pl-5">Vessels you can reuse for something else, afterward.</li>
        <li class="border-l border-[color:var(--color-ember)] pl-5">No marketing theatrics. Just the pour.</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
